{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dive into the Darkness and Uncover the Truth  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a pixelated world full of mysteries and dangers, you take on the role of a detective who won't stop at anything to solve the darkest cases. From tailing suspects in the shadows of the city to uncovering conspiracies that could shake the nation, every decision you make could be the difference between success and disaster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Do you have what it takes to discover the truth and survive the criminal underworld?</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Investigate, uncover, and reveal</strong>: Solve crimes across four cities filled with secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Travel and observe</strong>: Strategically move between cities and find key clues in every corner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Destroy or protect</strong>: Decide whether to expose the truth or bury it forever, destroy documents after reviewing looking for the name of the people involved in the job or the pictures of the people the client want to hide</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Photograph suspects in buildings:</strong> Look for the people to show in the windows and picture them to demostrate they are in the building, stadium or highways so that way the client can prove their words in the court</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Help police:</strong> Help in the police station identifying the guilty people though the window</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Travel and fun:</strong> Buy some useless but fun stuff in the metro to improve your car, your console game collection or read some books</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Time is ticking. Crime doesn't wait. It's time to act!</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255960/p